{ We are threatening ...dxe5 again. } 13. Nc3
{ White has no choice but to offer the e5-pawn to speed their development. }
13... dxe5 14. Nd5 Nxd5 15. Qxd5 Rd8
{ White recoups the pawn, but Black gets some development and the endgame is equal. }
