{ The bishop is not that useful on b4 anymore, since after Bxc3 White would always be more comfortable. Therefore, trading this bishop makes total sense. }
13. Rad1
{ This move doesn't change much in the position. We can have a look at my game against Hungaski. }
13... Be6 14. b3 Qc7 15. Bxd6 Qxd6 16. Qg3 Qxg3
{ With an equal endgame that I went on to win. } *

