{ Attacking d6 and c3.  16...Bxf2  17.Kxf2  followed by  17...Qb6  18.d4  and  18...Qxd6  looked good, but it does not work, as White has  19.Ba3  at the end of the line, winning the f8-rook. }
17. Nc4 Ba7
{ Black uses the fact that White cannot take on a5 and intends ...b5 to capture c3. If  18.Nxa5  Bb6  and if  18.Rxa5  b5  winning in both cases. }
18. Ba3 { Hitting the f8-rook. } 18... b5 19. Ne3
{ 19.Bxf8  was not possible due to  19...bxc4  and Black wins. } 19... a4
