16. cxd4
{ After  16.Qxd4  Qg5  , Black has some annoying threats like ...Nh4 or ...h5-h4 with a good kingside attack. }
16... d5 17. Qf3 Qh4
{ Black's pieces show great coordination, protecting each other and controlling important squares. }
