{ Now  10...Qd6  was not good due to  11.Bxc6  and Black has to play the sad move  11...bxc6  . }
11. exd5 Nd4 12. Nxe5 { It seems that White has snatched a pawn, but... } 12...
Bxh3 13. gxh3 Qg5+ { Black gets the piece back. } 14. Ng4 f5 15. f4 Qg6
{ Black will be a pawn down, but because of the strong d4-knight and White's weak king Black's position is better. }
