{ Stopping Ng4 and threatening dxe5, which would lead to the structure we should avoid. }
15... Nd7
{ Black is in time to protect the e5-pawn and now an interesting plan may be ...Ra5 to free the g6-knight and play ...Nf4. White has no easy way to make progress. }
