{ Black gains some space on the queenside with a tempo, thanks to the fact that  12.Qxa4  loses to  12...Bxf2+  and  12.Qxb7  is not possible due to  12...Qd7  and the white queen is trapped. }
12. Qc2 h6
{ Preventing Bg5. Next Black can improve their queen and rooks and maybe try to break with ...d5, whereas White's central break d4 is not easy to achieve. }
