{ Despite the missing piece, Black dominates the board. The white knight has practically no squares. }
15. Rf1 { The least harm is to save the rook instead of the knight. } 15...
cxd4 16. Bxd5 dxc3 17. Nxc3 Rc8
{ The material is equally balanced and the black has better pieces. } *

